data.description: This completely remodeled Ranch home you’ve been waiting for! This rare one has it all - updates, location, price!! Brand new PAID OFF solar panels so you don’t have an electric bill currently, NO HOA and plenty of driveway space so you can store your work vehicles, RVs, boats, campers etc. In addition to the 2 car garage. On almost a .25 acre lot with a brand new patio, and front yard landscaping. Quiet neighborhood with access to 2 large parks, trails, and Greenway Park Golf Course and Pool just around the corner. Also, shopping, restaurants, the Promenade Movie Theater, the Butterfly Pavilion, and the Westminster Rec. Quick access to Boulder and Denver. Newer roof and windows, new exterior and interior paint, new flooring, new kitchen with granite, gas stove, stainless appliances, modern bathrooms, new fans throughout, new swamp cooler and more. You will not get over the private backyard that was made for entertaining and grilling, and hanging out in the hot tub. The third bedroom upstairs can be an office or additional bedroom. Downstairs is finished with a large bedroom and bathroom, plus cozy living area, storage and laundry.
